cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.CY 

The paper discusses the interdisciplinary nature of Cognitive Science and its relation to fields such as psychology, linguistics, artificial intelligence, neuroscience, computer science, and philosophy. Based on this, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.AI (artificial intelligence), cs.CL (computation and language), cs.NE (neural and evolutionary computing), cs.LG (machine learning), and cs.CY (computers and society). These sub-categories cover the fields that are most closely related to Cognitive Science and are likely to be of interest to researchers in this area.
